condition_df = pd.DataFrame(data={CONDITION_ID: ['condition1', 'condition2'
    ], CONDITION_NAME: ['', 'Condition 2'], 'fixedParameter1': [1.0, 2.0]})
assert conditions.get_parametric_overrides(condition_df) == []
condition_df.fixedParameter1 = condition_df.fixedParameter1.values.astype(int)

condition_df.loc[0, 'fixedParameter1'] = 'parameterId'
